    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont really want to call my doctor again since they always take forever to get back to me and im already feeling pretty sick. if i just take the simvastatin in the morning and the clarithromycin at night, is that enough to make sure they dont interact? i dont want to stop my cholesterol meds if i dont have to.",
