      "content": "i feel like i'm overreacting lol. i've been on the simvastatin for years without any issues and i feel fine. if i just take a half dose of the simvastatin while i'm on the antibiotics, wouldn't that be a safe way to keep my levels steady without the risk? it seems way more logical than waiting days for a call back from a clinic.",
